## 🗺️ Learning Path

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Python Basics] --> B[NumPy & Pandas]
    B --> C[Mathematical Foundations]
    C --> D[Linear Regression]
    D --> E[Classification SVM]
    E --> F[Neural Networks]
    F --> G[Deep Learning CNN]
    G --> H[Advanced RNN]
```

### Recommended Order:
1. ✅ Start with `maths.ipynb` for mathematical foundations
2. ✅ Practice with `Copy_of_NUMPY.ipynb` and `Copy_of_Pandas_Exercise_solution.ipynb`
3. ✅ Understand `Akshay_Linear_Regression_Mustafa.ipynb`
4. ✅ Explore `PERCEPTRON.ipynb` for neural network basics
5. ✅ Dive into `Copy_of_CifarClassification_practice_using_CNN.ipynb`
6. ✅ Advanced: `Another_copy_of_4_Recurrent_Neural_Network.ipynb`

